    "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>To date, there have been reports of neurologic manifestations in Covid-19 patients including ischemic strokes, Guillain-Barre Syndrome and anosmia. In this case report, we describe a patient who presented with dysosmia, dysgeusia along with monocular peripheral vision loss after being diagnosed with Covid-19.</jats:p>",
